high_descs: Walk to the wall and look at the bed.
Pick up the pot from on the bed.
Walk out of the room with the pot and stop near the fridge.
Open the refrigerator and put the pot inside and then take the pot out.
Bring the pot back to the sidetable in the bedroom.
Put the pot on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Bring the Pot to the SideTable and cool it off before returning it.

high_descs: Walk to a sidetable next to a bed and face the bed.
Pick up a pot from the bed.
Turn around, leave the room through an exit on the left wall and in the upper corner, enter the space in the upper left of your view, and stand in front of a fridge on your right.
Put the pot inside the fridge, let it cool for a while, and then take it out.
Now go back to the sidetable.
Place the pot on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled pot on the sidetable.

high_descs: Head to the bed on the right.
Pick up the pot from the bed.
Turn right and turn left to head down the passage and reach the fridge on the right.
Cool the pot in the fridge and take it out.
Turn around and head right to reach the bedroom side table.
Put the pot on the side table.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled pot on the side table.
